<lyrics>[V1]
 1 - ḥb ạlmsyḥ ạ̉ṭybu
 lqlby min ʿṭf ạlbsẖr
 lqd fdạny bạldmạ
 wḥbũh lạ yndtẖr̊

[C1]
   ạlqrạr
   ạ̉sẖdw lh wạảṭrabu
   ḥbũ ạlmsyḥ ạ̉ṭybu
   mjdạ lh, sẖkrạ lh
   ḥbũ ạlmsyḥ ạ̉ṭybu

[V2]
 2 - ḥbũ ạlmsyḥ ạ̉ṭybu
 lqlby mn mạl wfyr
 gẖfrạnh, ḥḍwrh
 wuʿwdh tgẖny ạlfqyr

[V3]
 3 - ḥbũ ạlmsyḥ ạ̉ṭybu
 lqlby mn kẖmr ạlkrwm
 brwḥh ymlạủny
 bsẖrạ wạ̉frạḥạ tdwm</lyrics>
<title>ḥb ạlmsyḥ ạṭyb</title>
</song>